News.Title: Chamunda Electricals Limited: Shares Soar 40% on NSE SME Debut
News.Summary: Chamunda Electricals shares listed at ₹70 on NSE SME, a 40% premium over the IPO price of ₹50. The IPO, which closed with 737.97 times oversubscription, raised ₹14.60 crore. Proceeds will be used for capital expenditure, working capital, and debt repayment.
